{"tid":368512,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"再見！滿分的爸爸。","createTime":"2017-08-21T15:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T06:53:42.000Z","uid":131428,"like":1484,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e2ffb6a91f8a6a1513c39580fee24204af57923","tid":368512,"uid":131428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"今日爸爸肺癌走左<br />\n睇住佢今日抖氣起伏好大<br />\n平時好鐘意食野都冇胃口<br />\n不停話好辛苦好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不停叫護士幫佢打針加氧氣...<br />\n其實係個解脫<br />\n佢終於唔洗咁辛苦可以食好多好多野<br />\n謝謝您讓我做左22年公主...<br />\n細細個公司放晏您都特登趕黎小學送麥當當外賣;<br />\n自懂性以來每個星期日都帶我地周圍去family day; <br />\n讀書壓力大到失眠您會同我講分數高低不代表一切;<br />\n翻工比老細柄..您會氹我話您會幫我岀頭<br />\n您臨走前嗰幾個星期好辛苦好痛都特登賣左部車換部細車比我拎到車牌揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日再握住您隻手先發覺同我細個握嘅一樣..仍然係咁多枕...謝謝您 我最愛的爸爸<br />\n<br />\nBy 好愛好愛好愛您的女兒上"},{"pid":"3de31d8feb98a15e57934ccdf4215fe4480cf430","tid":368512,"uid":64840,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"你爸爸永遠都會活係你嘅心入面<br />\n<br />\nBe strong"},{"pid":"9dcfe75f0f3b83dbb0ac22accadfb1e2864f4c94","tid":368512,"uid":63935,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:08:34.000Z","msg":"你爸爸會見到呢個post既，睇到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ce4df8e718ccf4304e700e114a7821abcf0b79","tid":368512,"uid":45630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"爸爸係心入面永遠陪住你<br />\n<br />\nDeepest condolence to you and your family."},{"pid":"2e5c1a56984091797da1d385d49214ebd30fa567","tid":368512,"uid":80176,"like":11,"dislike":159,"score":-148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爸爸係心入面永遠陪住你<br />\n<br />\nDeepest condolence to you and your family.</blockquote><br />\n口德 +70"},{"pid":"23baa5bf677004ff2ef1405e52d38d21814c9411","tid":368512,"uid":97