20967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"加油呀 相信你爸爸最後一刻都係膽心你地怕你地冇左人照顧 ，你地成家要活得更堅強呀，唔好令佢在天之靈再擔心你地呀。<br />\n樓主依排要多啲陪下媽咪呀，相信佢係唔開心果個，有你係身邊支持佢相信佢會好快冇野<br />\n加油呀樓主 依度好多巴絲都會背後支持你"},{"pid":"96e30ebf6c500b52dc3cbd5729a0dde965d8ea38","tid":368512,"uid":131428,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Add oil sis<br />\n陪多d媽媽 有無兄弟姊妹</blockquote><br />\n有妹妹...其實一諗到對佢黎講舒服好多個心都無咁up...睇住佢辛苦，由日日都要飲杯奶茶先安落到買比佢都話飲完唔舒服...<br />\n希望佢去到嗰個世界係可以比佢盡情食...<br />\n遺憾係我岩岩先fresh grad趕唔切比佢享福<br />\n希望下世有緣再做佢個女"},{"pid":"9ebd084334c6ec340434bce12b694cbaee2bd9d2","tid":368512,"uid":64738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:08:48.000Z","msg":"加油啊！！！"},{"pid":"a5bf2bb5e37e8b529e7fa0f829ef3fea2bf7f432","tid":368512,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"大個女<br />\n往後ge路要靠自己"},{"pid":"e904c2c2f04a50a6f834595bc6513d68ca327457","tid":368512,"uid":23720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢會繼續幫你出頭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386988c42c67bc708738ab9c372faaffcd8eb94b","tid":368512,"uid":9121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:20:16.000Z","msg":"Be strong <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ddd05fc767b15e9d7679e2aefd7063d7a286fa","tid":368512,"uid":94834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda1c9b21e98ccf37032ccb5ea8a5823ccf29e71","tid":368512,"uid":59379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"stay strong and take care!!"},{"pid":"4e0efb22498e0607ea3824d6a8ff316638fc2d7e","tid